headline: EMCOR Group (EME) Sees EPS Surge as Net Income Climbs to US$241 Million
summary: EMCOR Group (EME) recently announced a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.25 per common share, to be paid on July 31, 2025. This steady dividend approach aligns with the company's robust quarterly performance, which saw net income rise to $241 million and EPS increase substantially year-over-year.
